room_title: Escape room "Mailroom Madness" by PuzzleMazement in Los Angeles

room_description: The Holy Grail has been found, but it's about to be hidden once more.  You've tracked it down to this post office.  You have one hour to recover it before it is lost for another 1,000 years.
